;THE ARGUMENT E IS A PRODUCT OF FACTORS SOME OF WHICH ARE NOT RPOBJECTS. THE
;FUNCTION RPOBS SEPARATES THESE AND PUTS THEM INTO NRPFACT.  THE RPFACTORS ARE
